      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KINGSBRAE EMMA (1) was in the placings last time but prior to that she posted a superb 25.30 win over 450m at this track. Expected to push the clock again here. RAPID LULU (2) jumped well to win over the 350m at this track two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing second at this track last start. Has performed well from this box with a win and six minor placings to her name from eight starts. Bold showing expected. SATRIANI (5) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 350m behind Rudolf Rumble (20.84) in a Grade 4/5. Worth following up. LIZ DUTTON (8) can find the frame without surprising.",
